Summary Table

Booking ID 		 : 123
Booking Given By : Empname, empID, designaation, department, company name
Car Details		 : Colour + Car Model, Car Number, 
Driver Details 	 : Driver Name, Phone 
Package Details  : Complete Table, Package Type, Name, Allowd Km, Allowed Hr

