Billing Codes

	Total & SubTotal 	=   1 to 100	
		Total Amount 	-	001
		SubTotal A 		-	011					
		SubTotal B 		-	012
		SubTotal C		-	013
		SubTotal D 		-   014

	Primary Rates		=	101 to 200
		Basic Rates  	-  	101					


	Travel Type Items 	=   201 to 300
		Fuel Surcharge  		-   201				
		Extra Km  				-   202	
		Extra Hr  				-   203 
		Driver Allowance		-   204  
		Night Hault Allowance 	- 	205  	
		Early Morning Charges 	- 	206 
		Night Charges  			-   207  

	Reimbursement Items =	301 to 400
		Toll 		 	-	301  
		Parking 		-	302


	Tax Items			=	401 to 500
		CSGT 			-	401
		SSGT 			-	402

	Negative Items 		=	901 to 999
		Discount		-	901
		Rounding Off 	-	902


