Bill Title
[_Single Trip Invoice__]

	Arrange the Expense Items as per their appearance on Invoice

	Expense Item Number		Billing Code
	1.  Basic Rates  	-  	101				x	^
	2.  Fuel Surcharge  -   201				x	|
	3.  Discount		-	901				x	|
	4.  SubTotal A 		-	011				x	v
	5.  Extra Km  		-   202				x
	6   Extra Hr  		-   203				x 
	7   Driver Allowance-   204				x  
	8   Night Hault Allowance - 205  		x
	9	Early Morning Charges - 206 		x
	10	Night Charges  	-   207  			x
	11	SubTotal B 		-	012				x
	12	CSGT 			-	401				x
	13  SSGT 			-	402				x
	14  SubTotal C		-	013				x
	15  Toll 		 	-	301  			x
	16  Parking 		-	302				x
	17  SubTotal D 		-   014				x
	17  Rounding Off 	-	902				x
	18  Total Amount 	-	001				x


	Formulae 	

	011 = 101 + 201 + (-1 x 901)
	012 = 202 + 203 + 204 + 205 + 206 + 207
	013 = 011 + 012 + 401 + 402
	014 = 301 + 302

	001 = 011 + 012 + 013 + 014 + 902

	902 = 011 - round(001,0) 



	Collection Name : billingSequence 
	{
		_id : xxx,
		billTitle : xxx,
		sequence : [
			{seqNum, billing code, }
			{seqNum, billing code, }
			{seqNum, billing code, }
		],
		createdBy : user_id,  (_id from users table for the logged in person)
		createdAt : Datetime,
		updateLog : [
			{updatedBy: user_id, updatedAt: datetime, remark: (to be added during update) }
		]

	}































